===========
CBOW vs Skip-Gram
-----------------

| Feature        | CBOW                        | Skip-Gram                 |
| -------------- | --------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| Input          | Context words               | Target word               |
| Output         | Target word                 | Context words             |
| Goal           | Predict the missing word    | Predict surrounding words |
| Training speed | Faster                      | Slower                    |
| Works well for | Frequent words              | Rare words                |
| Example        | "I love to ___ pizza" → eat | "eat" → love, to, pizza   |


